Html:
Hello.

In my project I want to click one of my button and the user can print the excel directly through the web printer,

(The excel has two sheets)

Is there any function ?

I have read the phpexcel developer documentation but I can not find it

please help

PHPExcel provides no mechanisms for actually generating a hardcopy paper printout of your worksheets: this is something that you will need to write yourself, dependent on your own printers. Do you meand print to a printer on the clients network or their PC? or print to a printer accessible from your webserver? What's the "web printer"?
